Burnt caramel colour. Medium carbonation. Rich, fruity over ripe aroma. Toasty, rich raisiny flavour with full but dry ester finish. Delicious. Makes you want to become monk. 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

The australian skateboarders beer of choice, so my first ever rating had to be this beer. Not as fruity or fragrant as other pale ales, but still a great go-to, easy drinking ale 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone
